#|
Proof: Let a = trunc-sqrt(n-2, x) and r = sticky-sqrt(x, n).
Suppose a^2 = x.  Then r = a, l^2 <= x = a^2 = r^2, and l <= r.  
By sticky-monotone, sticky-exactp-b, and exactp-trunc-sqrt,

  sticky(l, n) <= sticky(r, n) = r.

